.TH HYPRLAND\-RUN 1 "2025-11-20" "hyprland-guiutils 0.2.1" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprland\-run \- simple run dialog for Hyprland
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprland\-run
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprland\-run
is a simple GUI run dialog for Hyprland.
It provides a text input field where users can type an application name to
launch.
The executable is verified to exist in
.B $PATH
before launching.
.PP
Pressing Enter or clicking Run launches the application.
Pressing Escape closes the dialog.
.PP
The window class is
.BR hyprland\-run .
.SH OPTIONS
None.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Hyprland (1),
.BR hyprlauncher (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/hyprwm/hyprland-guiutils/issues
.UE .
